{"tid":2353894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅芯抗疫口罩開支涉2.8億元 剩餘6.2億元歸還防疫基金","createTime":"2021-01-05T05:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T05:48:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"11a2ce9ebf21b20969aa12b700c14f4365f17b47","tid":2353894,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"銅芯抗疫口罩開支涉2.8億元 剩餘6.2億元歸防疫基金<br />\n<br />\n政府向立法會提交「銅芯抗疫口罩」的核數報告，指當局最終購入1079萬個口罩，最終派發1032萬個，庫存47萬個。計劃原本預留8億元推展，但最終開支約是2.8億元，平均每個口罩涉及開支少於26元，計劃中有1億元由政府內部資源承擔，當局已將餘下6.2億元款項，歸還防疫抗疫基金。<br />\n<br />\n政府又指，今次的計劃是非牟利性質，紡織及成衣研發中心的相關開支是實報實銷，未用款項已陸續退還政府。研發中心亦已向供應商，原價退回部分尚未使用的原材料，並會以公開拍賣的方式，處理剩餘物資。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2373495&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=2a1c2536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373495</a>"},{"pid":"c9b16ce621d3792d52cf0582d988cbca31ebdb03","tid":2353894,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"26蚊個底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fae97533a5f9f08026481d3598a8d6a9313a33","tid":2353894,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"夠柒婆着一世，着唔曬燒俾佢落去着"}]}